dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: • This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:2,000,000 scale maps of East Asia, Australia, titled 'Nihyakumanbun no ichi Taiheiyō shūiki yochizu (kōkūzu) -- [1:2,000,000 Aerial Charts of the Pacific Rim] -- 二百萬分一太平洋周域輿地圖(航空圖)/Nihyakumanbun no ichi Taiheiyō shūiki yochizu (kōkūzu).’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
